{"tid":811492,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北韓建國70年慶典　棄武嚇凸顯經濟","createTime":"2018-09-09T01:00:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-09T02:49:54.000Z","uid":43041,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"063b9d4e1280d996df3fef55531e10f3b8886321","tid":811492,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T01:00:25.000Z","msg":"【北韓國慶】今日是北韓建國70周年，首都平壤有連串盛大的慶祝活動。領袖金正恩會如何利用這次外國記者雲集的機會，展示國家最新的發展方向，備受各方關注；雖然會有大型閱兵，但政治分析相信他不會藉此炫耀可以威脅美國本土的長程導彈，反而會重點凸顯過去一年的外交及發展經濟的決心。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180909/20495506\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180909%2F20495506&d=EeaBWpaP66fxj6hkiHlU7dr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=a974feaa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180909%2F20495506&h=2566f8f1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180909/20495506</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fcd695796ebf5f7832daa8c1cb701371d426922","tid":811492,"uid":82528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T02:20:06.000Z","msg":"北韓分明落支那面<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af54a52051ba7d601847d74a572d97d467d9c291","tid":811492,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T02:21:03.000Z","msg":"咁唔比面我國粟賤輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa68f6c558adf15d6646bcea881dfb19d5f09d7a","tid":811492,"uid":55386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T02:49:54.0